{
  "id": "adv_group_liz_03_03",
  "title": "LizNoir 03 03",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "…………三枝さん、私は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……Saegusa-san‚ I……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もう、その話は終わったと言っただろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told you that conversation is over.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.4773695945739744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "俺がバンプロに戻ることはない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not going back to Vanpro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.310702927907308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "（分かっていたことなのに。それにあの子……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I knew it. And that girl……)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.877369594573977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "……お姉ちゃん…………？\nまさか……あなた、長瀬麻奈の……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……Older sister…………？\nDon’t tell me…… You’re Mana Nagase’s……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.54403626124064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "はい……妹です……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes…… I’m her younger sister……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.20834471384684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "（長瀬琴乃――長瀬麻奈の妹が）\n（三枝さんのもとにいるなんて……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Kotono Nagase――Mana Nagase’s little sister)\n(is under Saegusa-san……)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.775011380513515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistaion-00-night",
      "startTime": 30.05626148184141
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistaion-00-night",
      "startTime": 30.056261481841442
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "まさかこんなことになるなんて\n思いもしなかったわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Never thought this would happen.\nI never imagined this……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.6750113805135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistaion-00-night",
      "startTime": 34.84167804718017
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "うん、長瀬麻奈の妹といきなり踊るなんて\n想定外過ぎだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ suddenly dancing with Mana Nagase’s little sister\nis way too unexpected.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.04167804718018,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistaion-00-night",
      "startTime": 41.0897549702571
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "勝手に現れて、勝手に逝って\n今度は妹……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She showed up on her own‚ left on her own‚\nand now her little sister……?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.0897549702571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistaion-00-night",
      "startTime": 46.35642163692377
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "長瀬麻奈、長瀬琴乃――\n貴方達姉妹はどうして邪魔ばかりするのよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana Nagase‚ Kotono Nagase――\nWhy are you sisters always getting in my way!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.85642163692377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistaion-00-night",
      "startTime": 53.698461795235296
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "莉央\nあの子達、僕達に全然ついてこれなかったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio\nThey couldn’t keep up with us at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.9984617952353,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "当然よ、素人同然だもの\n私達とはレベルが違い過ぎるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ they’re practically amateurs.\nThey’re on a completely different level from us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.69846179523531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistaion-00-night",
      "startTime": 63.398461795235306
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、おかしいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ it’s strange.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.39846179523531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistaion-00-night",
      "startTime": 66.2281896833426
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.2281896833426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "僕はちっとも嬉しくない\n気持ちがもやもやするんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not happy at all.\nMy feelings are muddled.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistaion-00-night",
      "startTime": 72.69485635000927
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "勝って当たり前だからじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn’t it because it’s only natural that we won?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.69485635000927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistaion-00-night",
      "startTime": 75.12818968334261
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.12818968334261,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "言いたいことがあるならはっきり言いなさいよ\n葵らしくもない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you have something to say‚ say it clearly.\nIt’s unlike you‚ Aoi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.93991309045217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistaion-00-night",
      "startTime": 82.72773055273753
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "僕はあの子達がうらやましかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was envious of them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.72773055273753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistaion-00-night",
      "startTime": 87.06516818243723
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "え……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.06516818243723,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんも、あの子達も凄く楽しそうだった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saegusa-san and those girls looked like they were having so much fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.26516818243722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistaion-00-night",
      "startTime": 93.48414754111032
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "僕も以前は踊ってるだけで楽しかったのに……\n今はなんだか違うんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I used to enjoy just dancing……\nbut now it’s different.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.35081420777692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistaion-00-night",
      "startTime": 100.23319539267277
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "姫野さんが余計な仕事を\n取ってくるからじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn’t it because Himeno-san brings us\nextra work?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.76652872600611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "そうかもしれないけど……\nうーん、何かが変わっちゃったのかな、僕",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe……\nHmm‚ did something change‚ I wonder?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.83319539267276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistaion-00-night",
      "startTime": 111.15545560326373
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "葵、LizNoirはプロよ\nプロは楽しいだけじゃやっていけないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi‚ LizNoir is professional.\nProfessionals can’t just do things because it’s fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.92212226993028,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistaion-00-night",
      "startTime": 116.98878893659696
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_03-rio015.m4a",
